<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Cache_Backend_Sqlite depends on the PHP extension '{{sqlite}}', not PDO_SQLITE as supposed by Zend_Cache_AllTests that I wrote recently.</p>

<p>Please skip Sqlite tests if the '{{sqlite}}' extension is not present.</p>

<p>Please write code in the Zend_Cache_Backend_Sqlite class to detect when the extension is not present, and throw an informative exception instead of aborting the process with a fatal error about a missing method '{{sqlite_open()}}'.</p>

